[thinking] **Considering test class structure**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I'm thinking about adding stub jar to the app classpath at runtime, but that doesn't work. Compiling test fixture classes into test classes does. Maybe I could try using a custom processor string, but some lines are hardcoded and can't be configured. Mockito doesn't seem to be the answer either. The user mentioned having coverage in dedicated Java test files, so I’m wondering if we could manage with non-test support classes while maintaining public access for package imports.
